# Conventional Commits Template
# 
# Type: Description (50 chars max)
#
# Types:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix  
#   docs:     Documentation changes
#   style:    Code style changes (formatting, etc.)
#   refactor: Code refactoring without functional changes
#   perf:     Performance improvements
#   test:     Adding or fixing tests
#   chore:    Build process, dependencies, etc.
#   ci:       CI/CD changes
#   security: Security improvements
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add session idle timeout with 8-hour default
#   fix: resolve race condition in cache operations
#   docs: update README with installation instructions
#   security: implement peer credential validation
#
# Optional body (wrap at 72 chars):

# Optional footer:
# Breaking Change: describe any breaking changes
# Closes #123: reference issue numbers